title: A 2018 Winter Solstice Ceremony (2018-12-19)
itunes:title: A 2018 Winter Solstice Ceremony
description: A 2018 Winter Solstice Ceremony (2018-12-19) - La Sarmiento and Alli Mosehauer perform dharma spoof songs for the 2018 IMCW Solstice Celebration, followed by a candle light ceremony with Tara and the Insight Meditation Community of Washington (IMCW) community.
